{"tid":1747551,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"G持港獨既有可能係間諜","createTime":"2019-11-23T09:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:54:44.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0ced03be1f5d48ef086e1729707e14f493206887","tid":1747551,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n「我以愛國主義影響他們，指導他們愛國、愛黨和中共領導人，並強烈反對支持香港獨立和進行民主活動的人士。」他的組織對香港民主運動的領導人進行了網絡攻擊和肢體攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n王說中共還派人混入活動人士中：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們派一些學生加入學生會，讓他們假裝支持香港獨立</span>。」「他們找到了那些支持獨立運動的人士的信息&hellip;&hellip;並公開了他們的所有個人數據、父母和家人的信息。」<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔係講緊近呢幾個月既事，<br />\n黃之鋒？熱狗？"},{"pid":"4c78df7b64aa38f17bfff5228f6298a237861825","tid":1747551,"uid":261332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"熱狗近排幫手維穩露骨到直頭連掩飾都廢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪收到風就黎穿煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc756face8028a12d4f4c073afc8ca5bd78275f","tid":1747551,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52fcea78d74de2ce6dfddeecb0e683e39a6f8554","tid":1747551,"uid":251052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"捉鬼就真係中計啦"},{"pid":"e596dbfe1fc01485bceb63bbe5deb750aca5fcac","tid":1747551,"uid":6070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"梁天琦"},{"pid":"86924475936ccfeb8adcc512586c438f1c5c83b1","tid":1747551,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n熱狗反對香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n出po之前可唔可以做下資料搜集"},{"pid":"3ea2cee42d6026f987e1e15652a84